info.author: Chris Miles
classifiers: Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries :: Python Modules
info.description:
A Python package providing an abstraction around a
filesystem-based queue. All queue operations are
atomic as they rely on directory operations, so
it is commonly used as a persistent queue between
services.
info.name: DirectoryQueue
info.summary: A simple filesystem-based persistent queuing abstraction.
